OL,6,FMiddlesbrough Council has been granted
OL,7,Fexceptional funding from the
OL,8,Fgovernment of more than #13 million.
OL,10,FThe additional support has been agreed
OL,11,Fin principle after the council
OL,13,FThe council has a #4.7m budget gap
OL,14,Fafter proposing a number of cost-
OL,15,Fcutting measures to try and balance
OL,16,Fits books. It is also proposing a
OL,17,F4.99% rise in council tax.
OL,19,FMiddlesbrough Mayor Chris Cooke said:
OL,20,F"This is welcome news and key to our
OL,21,Fbudget setting for 2024/25.
